thread.title: VPBE

author: Tylobic
title: VPBE
text: Active Void Gate duration and cooldown reduced to 120 seconds from 150. Voidlings: Health growth reduced to 0 from 50. Current health decay per tick increased to 20% from 10% . Structure damage increased to 20 - 360 (based on level) from 5 - 90 (based on level) . Removed: Killing Voidings increases creep score by one. Upcoming Changes Edit Pentakil 2nd Album Praeco has tweeted out a small teaser for the next PENTAKILL album. He also noted that the vocalist on the track is Jorn Lande. [1] [2] Previews of the album were also played during the concert at League Fest. [3] References
